<figureCitation id="9AED8A176B58EF031D6A9871556FFC73" captionStart="Figures 49–54" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figures 49 - 54. Type materials, scale bars = 2.0 mm: 49 Lectotype of Allocota caerulea Andrewes [= Allocota viridipennis Motschulsky] 50 Holotype of Allocota cyanipennis Heller 51 Lectotype of Taicona aurata Bates [= Allocota aurata (Bates)] 52 Holotype of Allocota bicolor sp. n. 53 Syntype of Dasiosoma testaceum Britton 54 Holotype of Dasiosoma hirsutum Basilewsky [= Dasiosoma basilewskyi nom. n.]." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29682" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Fig. 50</figureCitation>
